description: This file initializes the React application by rendering the 'App' component into the DOM element with id 'root'. It sets up the React root, applies strict mode, and imports core dependencies, styles, and the main App component.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering the React component tree into a DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React element tree into the created root.
